                            **** N O T E S ****

IMDB lists the movie with a runtime of 102mins.
This is the duration of the film (projected at 24fps)
My encode's duration is 98mins.
The 4mins difference is due to PAL's 4% Speedup.

PAL's 4% Speedup: A Film is projected at 24fps. PAL DVDs project at 25fps.
As a result, the movie runs 4% faster.
Hence the 4 mins difference between my encode (source was a PAL DVD at 25fps) and the runtime listed at IMDB.

Google around for more info :)
